            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm md:text-base mt-3 lg:leading-7 text-justify"><strong>Google Analytics.</strong> We use Google Analytics to collect and store data that enables us to analyse the use of our Service. Google Analytics collects and stores statistical and other information about website use by means of cookies, which are stored on users’ computers. Certain advertising features have been enabled that may collect data via the user of advertising cookies and anonymous identifiers Google Analytics Demographics &amp; Interest Reporting To prevent your data being collected by Google Analytics you may opt-out via Google Analytics’<!-- --> <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="text-custom-green underline" href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout/ ">currently available opt-outs</a> <!-- -->for the web. Google’s privacy policy is available at:<!-- --> <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="text-custom-green underline" href="">https://www.google.com/policies/privacy/.</a></p>
