        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm md:text-base mt-3 lg:leading-7 text-justify">Based on the applicable laws of your country, you may have the right to request access to the personal information we collect from you, change that information, or delete it in some circumstances. To request to review, update, or delete your personal information, please visit your profile page or mail us at:<!-- --> <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="text-custom-green underline" href="mailto:feedback@flatmate.in">feedback@flatmate.in</a></p>
