        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm md:text-base mt-3 lg:leading-7 text-justify">- Our Sites and Services may also deliver notifications to your phone or mobile device, where you have consented to such communications. You can disable these notifications by changing the settings on your mobile device.</p>
