        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm md:text-base mt-3 lg:leading-7 text-justify"><strong>No Rights of Third Parties. </strong>This Privacy Policy does not create rights enforceable by third parties or require disclosure of any personal information relating to users of the website.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm md:text-base mt-3 lg:leading-7 text-justify"><strong>Changes to this Privacy Policy. </strong>We will occasionally update this Privacy Policy. When we post changes to this Privacy Policy, we will revise the “last updated” date at the top of this Privacy Policy. We recommend that you check our Sites from time to time to inform yourself of any changes in this Privacy Policy or any of our other policies.</p>
